  <official_title>An 8-week Multi-center, Dose Escalation Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Aliskiren (150 mg and 300 mg) Administered Alone and in Combination With Valsartan (160 mg and 320 mg) in Patients With Hypertension</official_title>
